            "content": "<p>Once the product is <strong>successfully picked up</strong>, the refund is <strong>processed within 48 to 72 working hours</strong> from our end. Once the refund is processed, you will receive a refund notification at your registered email address. It takes 5 to 7 working days for the amount to be credited to your bank account. If the refund is not <strong>processed </strong>within this timeframe, please reach out to the <strong>customer support</strong> team for assistance.</p>",
